data.description: One or more photo(s) has been virtually staged. Immerse yourself in the unparalleled coastal charm of Belleair Beach with this exquisite beach home. Where you can indulge in tranquil white-sand beaches and crystal-clear waters, just a short stroll away from your doorstep. Embrace the exclusive ambiance of Belleair Beach's upscale residential neighborhoods, that offer a sanctuary of peace and privacy, while still providing easy access to an array of cultural attractions, dining options, and entertainment. With a quick turn and 60 second drive from Gulf Blvd and Belleair Beach - you'll find 115 13th St. This wonderful single story house is a durable Rutenberg block construction build. The picturesque front patio and Mediterranean inspired tile roof add to the charm and great curb appeal. Step inside the gorgeous stained glass double doors to a spacious two bedroom two bath home and discover a meticulously maintained residence. Adorned with tasteful upgrades and thoughtful details throughout. The spacious split-plan layout boasts ample room for both relaxation and entertainment. You'll find a cozy den featuring a charming wood-burning fireplace for intimate gatherings and a spacious sunroom and backyard oasis for large parties. The expansive Florida room brings in great natural sunlight and offers beautiful views of the pool and inviting yard. Outside, the sparkling saltwater pool is surrounded by a fenced backyard and low-maintenance tropical landscaping. Offering a private retreat for leisurely afternoons and lively gatherings alike. There is also a weather tracking station and a convenient rainwater preservation system. A sizable attached 2 car garage and indoor laundry room offer ample storage for this home as well. This must see property is situated within close proximity to a wealth of amenities, including restaurants, boutique shops, waterfront parks and recreational facilities. It presents an opportunity to experience the quintessential Belleair Beach lifestyle. Don't miss your chance to make this coastal retreat your own. Schedule a viewing today and discover the endless possibilities that await!     Property Features: Two bedrooms, Two bathrooms, Two car garage, Split Bedroom Floor Plan, Tile Roof, Stained Glass Double Door Entry, Den/Bonus Room with built in shelving, Wood Burning Fireplace with Stainless Steel chimney liner, Expansive Florida Sunroom with Kitchen pass-through, Laundry Room with pantry space, Insulated Double-Pane Slider Doors, French doors to Sunroom, Plantation Window Shutters, Ceramic Tile Flooring throughout, Rain Barrel Water Preservation System, Weather Tracking Station, Saltwater Pool - Recently resurfaced, Irrigation Sprinkler System, 2023 Plumbing CIPP Lining/Coating with Transferrable Warranty, Dishwasher 2023, New Backyard Fencing, 2021 Electric Water Heater, Rutenberg Block Construction    Nearby:Belleair Beach Access- 5min Walk. Parking available only to Belleair Residents. Bayside Park -15min Walk/5min Bike. With Tennis/Pickleball Courts, Playground, Small Sand Beach Area. Belleair Causeway Boat Ramp - 10min Bike/5min Drive. Waterfront Parks -16th and 20th St in walking distance. Publix Grocery - 5min Drive across Belleair Bridge. Clearwater Marina and Pier 60 Activities - 10min Drive.
